name: Empowered Waifu #2
description:
Description: "We Can Do It." There is nothing in this world that these waifus can't do for you.

Mary had a little lamb, now she runs her own farm. Wealth is not her concern but the way you live so humbly made her want to take care of you. She's undeniably busy, but always makes time to cook your dinner. All she wants is you living as healthy as her cows.
